HEADWORD: geezer
<hw>gee"zer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Dial. corrupt. of
<er>Guiser</er> a mummer.]</ety> <def>A queer old fellow; an old chap;
sometimes, an old woman.</def> <mark>[Contemptuous, Slang.]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bloke.</syn>⟦br⟧
